      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "此事何劳先生亲自驾临。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00019",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "故旧之谊，聊表鄙意。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00020",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "肃真乃钦佩。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00021",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "先灵供奉何处？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00022",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "现在后堂。前面带路。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00023",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "有劳大夫。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00024",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "诸葛亮、鲁肃同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00025",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套同上，诸葛亮、鲁肃、赵云同上。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00026",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "见陵寝不由人泪如雨降，想遗容倒叫我寸断肝肠。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00027",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "叫哭",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "哎，都督吓！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00028",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "可怜你钟山秀青年在望，可怜你美英雄一旦夭亡。可怜你兢业业一生空禳，可怜你忙碌碌半世奔忙。实指望灭曹瞒安乐共享，又谁知大数到已作魍魉！",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00029",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "赵云"
      ],
      "text": "“呜呼公瑾，不幸夭亡；修短由天，人岂不伤。我心实痛，酹酒一觞；君其有灵，享我蒸尝。从此天下，与谁相商。呜呼痛哉，伏维尚享。”",
      "text_length": 62
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00030",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "哎，都督吓！想你英雄盖世，一代传人，贯精忠于日月，秉赤胆于东方，不幸一旦身亡。哎，好不遗恨人也。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00031",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "反二黄慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "你是个创业的忠贞良将，你是个振东方豪杰贤良。谁似你天生成高致雅量，谁似你文武略气宇轩昂？谁似你年弱冠兵权独掌，谁似你兴霸业扶弱抑强？奸曹操统雄兵如风似浪，只唬得众儿郎束手要降。若非你怀大志陈兵相抗，用机谋杀得他弃甲丢枪！到如今少得遂太平景象，转瞬间天不佑大厦断梁。抛得吾孤人儿将谁依傍，将谁依傍？都督吓！",
      "text_length": 152
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00032",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四吴将同上，同打把。鲁肃拦下。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00033",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "反二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "抛得吾独一人谁作商量？吾和你好一比伯仲情况，吾和你好一比鸡黍范张。望阴魂鉴吾这虔诚祭享，泪汪汪捧玉樽享受蒸尝。",
      "text_length": 55
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00034",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "呜呼公谨，不幸夭亡。呜呼痛哉，伏维尚享！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00035",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "到如今奸曹在你先自丧，抛得吾无前后好不悲伤！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00036",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "吓！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00037",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "思至此只哭的咽喉气丧，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00038",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "见先生只哭得我好悲伤。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00039",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "先生不必啼哭，保重身体要紧。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00040",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "咳，看此光景，泪出肺腑，纵有千言万语，一时难禁！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00041",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "破曹之事，仰仗先生。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00042",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "列公既以奸曹为念，亮当谨记于心，同力破曹为上。告辞。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00043",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "后帐备得水酒，与先生同饮。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00044",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "原当领受，奈公务在身。公谨哪，你若有灵，须鉴吾心哪！",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00045",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "心问口口问心牢骚千丈，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00046",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四吴将自两边分上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00047",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "有万篇诉不尽腹内悲伤。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00048",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "送先生。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00049",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "送千里终须别何劳过让，试看吾一帆风雨洒康庄。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00050",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵云、诸葛亮同下。四龙套、周循同上。周循祭灵。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00051",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周循"
      ],
      "text": "何人前来吊祭？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00052",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "诸葛先生前来吊祭。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00053",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周循"
      ],
      "text": "为何不将他拿下，与我父报仇？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00054",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "他祭了又哭，哭了又祭。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00055",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周循"
      ],
      "text": "几时去的？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00056",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "方才去的。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00057",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周循"
      ],
      "text": "待我将他赶上！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00058",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "且慢，那孔明用兵如神，又有赵云跟随，若是动手，又恐他变。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00059",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周循"
      ],
      "text": "不必拦阻，众将官，追！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00060",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、周循同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00061",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵云、诸葛亮同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00062",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "笑",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈哈……",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00063",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "非是我笑他人无有志量，怎知我袖儿里暗有形藏。遇不着智谋人心中惆怅，",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00064",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "庞统上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00065",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "庞统"
      ],
      "text": "纵有那托天手难逃我掌。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00066",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庞统"
      ],
      "text": "好吓，你将我周都督气死，来到灵前，假意吊孝，明欺我东吴无人。来来来，我与你分个上下。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00067",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "吓，原来是凤雏先生！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00068",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "同笑",
      "speakers": [
        "庞统",
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈哈……",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00069",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "吓，凤雏，我量你计谋不能尽用，足下何不投一明君，不负生平所愿。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00070",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庞统"
      ],
      "text": "我意欲投一明君，没有引见之人。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00071",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "先生吓，吾今此来，实为老兄。吾观孙仲谋，不能重用足下。吾主宽仁厚义，不负生平所学。我已修下荐书，趁便既往荆州，共扶汉业，名垂千古，岂不美哉？",
      "text_length": 70
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00072",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庞统"
      ],
      "text": "多蒙先生举荐，我当照行。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00073",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "内呐喊声。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00074",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庞统"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，后面尘土冲天，东吴追兵来也。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00075",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "不妨，我自有敌他之兵。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00076",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庞统"
      ],
      "text": "后日再叙，告辞了。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00077",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "请。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00078",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "庞统下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00079",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "想人生荣与枯得失难量，际风云显奇谋姓字名扬。远望着白泛泛滔天波浪，",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00080",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张飞上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00081",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "张翼德驾小舟迎接先生。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00082",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "搭了扶手。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00083",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "诸葛亮、赵云同上船。周循、鲁肃、四龙套同上。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00084",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周循"
      ],
      "text": "舟中敢是诸葛先生？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00085",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "然也。你乃何人？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00086",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周循"
      ],
      "text": "俺乃周都督之子，名唤周循。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00087",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "到此何干？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00088",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周循"
      ],
      "text": "闻得先生前来吊祭，特地前来谢孝。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00089",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "既为谢孝而来，为何持戈相向？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00090",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周循"
      ],
      "text": "这个……请先生过船，有话相商。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00091",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "吾要过船，这恐怕小性命，也要随你父去也。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00092",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周循"
      ],
      "text": "众将官，杀！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00093",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "呔！我把你这小奴才，来在长江追杀奠客，本当一箭将你杀死，念你乃是犯孽身重之人，便宜你这王八肏的！三军的催舟。",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00094",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "大夫！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00095",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "哦，先生。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00096",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "笑",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈哈……",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00097",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张飞、赵云、诸葛亮同下。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00098",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周循"
      ],
      "text": "且住。今日到被他们羞辱一场，待我投江一死罢！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00099",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "text": "且慢。你我回至柴桑，整顿人马，再与都督报仇！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01001019_e00100",
      "play_id": "01001019",
      "scene_id": "01001019_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}